column55:
During a visit to this planet on 6 June 2019, a freighter fleet warped into the system and miscalculated their warp coordinates.  The fleet warped directly into the moon surface, likely resulting in the deaths of hundreds if not more crew members.  The results of this terrible accident can be seen in the 'Scenery' gallery.

Also of note, the system [[Space Station]] can be clearly seen from the planet surface due to its proximity to the atmosphere. See the Info gallery for an illustration.
